#, no-c-format
msgid "Signs"
msgstr "Les panneaux"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sign HTML:"
msgstr "Panneaux HTML :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter any valid &HTML; here. For example, entering <userinput>Hit it "
"&lt;i&gt;softly&lt;/i&gt; towards the slope!</userinput> will create the "
"text <quote>Hit it <emphasis>softly</emphasis> towards the slope!</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez saisir ici tout HTML valable. Par exemple, saisissez "
"<userinput>Frappez &lt;i&gt;doucement&lt;/i&gt; en direction de la pente !</"
"userinput> affichera le texte <quote>Frappez <emphasis>doucement</emphasis> "
"en direction de la pente !</quote>"

